__Requiring approval for PRs by protecting branches__
https://help.github.com/en/github/administering-a-repository/enabling-required-reviews-for-pull-requests
Summary:
1. Go to repo settings
2. Select protect branch (usually for master)
3. check require PR reviews before merging
4. check dismiss stale PR approvals
5. check applied to admins

